column36:
Okta OIDC configuration Webpage shows the Redirect URI text field to contain a hint of:


{noformat}/OIDCResponse/data{noformat}



This is not correct as validated in CI 10.09.000 HF2



It should follow a hint as the following:

{noformat}https://<CI Host>/api/OIDCToken/OIDCResponse{noformat}

