column405:
10-08-2024 5:46 PM;61a0843c3618cd006fa23906;For the mentioned issue we have applied the improvised smservice API and SDK bot patch along with the new connector file for O365 shared by Shrikant on DT's environment and the recon for fetching DIs began on Friday.Ā

As of Friday evening, the Admin console page displayed 14,865 digital identities. However, the page shows a "no Data found" message. Upon further analysis, we discovered that the page displays 499 errors due to timeout issues with the API calls. The same has been showcased to @Akhil SainathĀand @Shrikant ShedekarĀover the session.

@Akhil Sainath, as discussed, kindly confirm with us the necessary changes for the issue to be resolved as soon as possible, as the client is following up on this.

